rows.label: tlk70000008_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I was saying before how the squad had
gone downhill. But it's picked up a bit
lately. Everyone doing their bit.

rows.label: tlk70000008_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I guess with the state of the world
lately, even those layabouts had to
change their tune.

rows.label: tlk70000008_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Sure, we've had a few leave, but we've
also been getting some new blood.
And that's real good for the squad.

rows.label: tlk70000008_05_msg0004
rows.name:
This lot might not be the toughest in
the world, but they know what they're
fighting for. And that's a good start.

rows.label: tlk70000008_05_msg0005
rows.name:
It's no good if you don't know what
you've got till it's gone. We need
people who are smarter than that!
